el Kiwanuka</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duran-duran">Duran Duran</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paolo-nutini">Paolo Nutini</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-cell">Soft Cell</a>一同亮相 Lake Stage。和更多。</p><p>舞台开幕日的艺术家尚未确定。</p><p>与此同时，Casino Stage 节目“模糊了爵士乐、非洲节奏、流行音乐和说唱乐之间的界限”。描述补充道：“这种亲密的环境沉浸在音乐历史中，也被证明是知名艺术家展示特殊、独特项目的理想舞台。”</p><p>整个音乐节期间， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dionne-warwick">Dionne Warwick</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andre-3000">André 3000</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paloma-faith">Paloma Faith</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noname">Noname</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mahalia">Mahalia</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brittany-howard">Brittany Howard</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loreen">Loreen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/d4vd">D4vd</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyla">Tyla</a>和 Thee Sacred Souls 等乐队将接管这个场地。</p><p>此外，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">Pink Floyd</a>鼓手 Nick Mason 将于 7 月 13 日将他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/features/music-features/pink-floyd-nick-mason-saucerful-secrets-australia-tour-2023-dates-tickets-teg-dainty-3434991">Saucerful Of Secrets</a>项目带到 Casino Stage。 </p><figure id="attachment_3619528" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3619528" style="width: 1164px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3619528" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MontreuxJazzFestival-2024-line-up.jpg" alt="2024 年蒙特勒爵士音乐节阵容" width="1164" height="1662" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MontreuxJazzFestival-2024-line-up.jpg 1164w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MontreuxJazzFestival-2024-line-up-400x571.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MontreuxJazzFestival-2024-line-up-800x1142.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/MontreuxJazzFestival-2024-line-up-696x994.jpg 696